content: The app has many annoying usability issues. E.g. when entering a payment the last step only allows you to confirm or cancel. If you have a small mistake there is no way to correct it, you have to cancel and enter all from scratch. Another issue is that in some views only short account numbers are displayed rather than names. Inconsistent: certain functions are available from certain places but not from other places. E.g. scanned payment slips. There are many other problems like these. Overall: overloaded with features, overcomplicated and not user friendly. This application looks like a "technical app" for developers rather than end users. Please make it simpler and develop a usability concept!
replyContent: After you controlled all the information you can still go back with the arrow on the top left corner to edit the information of your payment.
